data.description: Welcome to 1265 Poplar Ridge Rd, Alexandria! Ranch style 3 bed, 2.5 bath nestled on a large .43 acre lot! Beautiful and large yard will make you feel like you are in the country but with the conveniences of the city. Additional features include hardwood floors, kitchen w/island & butlers pantry, bay widow, loads of closets for storage, office space, lg LL laundry room, walkout basement, 2 driveways, front porch, rear brick patio & lovely landscaping!
